title: About
text: Hello, my name is Tysen Christie and I am a 21-year-old Sports Media Major at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln. I am originally from Lincoln, Nebraska and in my free time I like to watch sports or do anything involving sports, especially with friends.

title: Do Elite NFL Offenses or Defenses Succeed More?
text:
